\vspace*{3mm}
\begin{center}
{\Large  Area spectrum and quasinormal modes of black holes\\}
\vspace*{12mm}
\large Alexios P. Polychronakos\footnote{On leave from Physics Department,
University of Ioannina, Greece.} \\
\vspace*{5mm}
{\em Physics Department, Baruch College of CUNY\\
New York, NY 10010, USA\\
\small alexios@gursey.baruch.cuny.edu \/}\\
\vspace*{4mm}
\vspace*{15mm}
\end{center}
%\maketitle


\begin{abstract}
We demonstrate that an equidistant area spectrum for the link variables
in loop quantum gravity can reproduce both the thermodynamics and 
the quasinormal mode properties of black holes.

\end{abstract}


\
